    "disabled": false,
    "info": "Compile the TypeScript writer runtime for Delta_280_ss40k and send writes to PCS.SYSTEM_ACTIVE_POWER_DEMAND. Update the Modbus client host/port/unitId before use.\n\nRecommended sequence:\n1. Set PCS Modbus client IP/port/unitId\n2. Press Compile PCS Writer\n3. Press one of the write injects (25 kW / -25 kW / 0 kW)\n4. Watch Write Requests / Modbus Write Result / Diagnostics"
